      Guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Check if you can claim the Job Support Scheme
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Find out if you're eligible and how much you can claim towards the cost of an employee's wages for hours they've not worked due to coronavirus (COVID-19).</p>

  </div>
</div>

